metrics.name: ChannelState_AdapterDao.getBrandState
metrics.sql: select t0.channel, t0.when_last_orders_polled, t0.when_last_cancel_polled from mp_channel t0 where t0.channel = ?

metrics.name: ChannelAts_AtsListener.publishAts
metrics.sql: select t0.channel, t0.sku, t0.quantity from mp_ats_channel t0 where (t0.channel = ? and t0.sku = ?)

metrics.name: MarketplaceShipment_ShipmentDao.getIdsOfUnsentShipmentsCreatedBefore
metrics.sql: select t0.id from mp_shipment t0 where t0.when_sent is null and (t0.when_created < ? or t0.when_created is null)

metrics.name: MarketplaceOrder_AdapterDao.findUnconfirmedOrders
metrics.sql: select t0.order_id, t0.update_sent, t0.last_mp_status, t0.last_internal_status, t0.when_updated, t0.fk_channel from mp_order t0 where t0.last_internal_status = any(?) and t0.fk_channel = ? and t0.last_mp_status = any(?)

metrics.name: MarketplaceShipment_ShipmentDao.getShippingNoticesToSend
metrics.sql: select t0.id, t0.consignment, t0.when_sent, t0.retries_attempted, t0.when_created, t0.order_id from mp_shipment t0 left join mp_order t1 on t1.order_id = t0.order_id  where t0.when_sent is null and (t0.retries_attempted < ? or t0.retries_attempted is null) and t1.fk_channel = ?

metrics.name: CancelGroup_AdapterDao.findInternalCancelGroupRequests
metrics.sql: select t0.id, t0.cancel_key, t0.when_received, t0.when_processed, t0.when_replied_to_tmp, t0.internal_cancel_response, t0.when_confirmed, t0.cancel_raw, t0.cancel_raw_class, t0.status, t0.order_id from mp_cancel_group t0 left join mp_order t1 on t1.order_id = t0.order_id  where t0.internal_cancel_response = any(?) and t1.fk_channel = ? and t0.when_replied_to_tmp is null and t1.last_mp_status = any(?) and t0.status is null

metrics.name: MarketplaceOrder_AdapterDao.findUnexportedOrders
metrics.sql: select t0.order_id, t0.update_sent, t0.last_mp_status, t0.last_internal_status, t0.when_updated, t0.fk_channel from mp_order t0 where t0.fk_channel = ? and t0.last_mp_status = any(?) and t0.update_sent = ?

metrics.name: CancelGroup_AdapterDao.findResponsesReadyForMarketplace
metrics.sql: select t0.id, t0.cancel_key, t0.when_received, t0.when_processed, t0.when_replied_to_tmp, t0.internal_cancel_response, t0.when_confirmed, t0.cancel_raw, t0.cancel_raw_class, t0.status, t0.order_id from mp_cancel_group t0 left join mp_order t1 on t1.order_id = t0.order_id  where t0.internal_cancel_response = any(?) and t1.fk_channel = ? and t0.when_replied_to_tmp is null and t0.status = ?

metrics.name: ChannelState_AdapterDao.updateLastPolledForOrders
metrics.sql: update mp_channel set when_last_orders_polled=? where channel = ?

metrics.name: CancelGroup_AdapterDao.findRequestedCancelsNotSent
metrics.sql: select t0.id, t0.cancel_key, t0.when_received, t0.when_processed, t0.when_replied_to_tmp, t0.internal_cancel_response, t0.when_confirmed, t0.cancel_raw, t0.cancel_raw_class, t0.status, t0.order_id from mp_cancel_group t0 left join mp_order t1 on t1.order_id = t0.order_id  where t0.internal_cancel_response is null and t1.fk_channel = ? and t1.last_internal_status = any(?) and t0.status = ?
